title: 01/08/21 - HOUR 3 - Adam Thielen
itunes:title: 01/08/21 - HOUR 3 - Adam Thielen
description:
The guys wrap up the final hour with a discussion about Rookie QBs. Justin Herbert may not be who we think he is, only time to well. Minnesota Vikings, Adam Thielen joins the show to talk about his love hate relationship with the Green Bay Packers, trash talk amongst players on the field and more!
